::Striker::

Striker continues to lead Spears toward the valley which he had in mind. He 
had found it while doing patrolls, back in the time when the Ark was still in 
good condition, and the Alliance was on the Maximals' side. He glances at 
Spears, walking beside him.

Suddenly an urge to pick her up over comes him (my chars have been having 
lot's of urge's lately, havn't they?), Striker not resisiting it one bit as 
he swoops Spears off her feet with a quick motion, picking her up and hoping 
that she wouldn't resist.
